<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:justify'><a style='mso-endnote-id:edn1' href="#_ednref1" name="_edn1" title=""><span style='font-size:11.0pt'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">     </span></span></a><span class="MsoEndnoteReference"><span style='font-size:11.0pt'>*</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">  </span>Retired Judge Robert L. Lobrano, assigned as
