</div>

<div style='mso-element:endnote' id="edn3">

<p class="MsoNormal" style='margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:justify'><a style='mso-endnote-id:edn3' href="#_ednref3" name="_edn3" title=""><span style='font-size:11.0pt'><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">     </span></span></a><span class="MsoEndnoteReference"><span style='font-size:11.0pt'>2</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span>In response to WTP’s suit, respondents
filed an exception of no cause of action. The trial court maintained the
